<para style="p">A psalm of David, to bring to remembrance.</para>

<para style="b" />

<para style="q1">

<verse number="1" style="v" />Yahweh, do not rebuke me in your anger;</para>

<para style="q1">do not punish me in your wrath.</para>

<para style="q1">

<verse number="2" style="v" />For your arrows pierce me,</para>

<para style="q1">and your hand presses me down.</para>
